title: Downtown San Jose development designed to lure high-tech companies
text: The Museum Place project combines an expansion of the Tech Museum of Innovation, reuse of Parkside Hall and a 270 foot high-rise tower with office space, 185 residential units, retail and a boutique hotel with penthouses on the top three floors. ...
